                <property name="margin-start">4</property>
                <property name="label" translatable="yes">For these fields, enter a number between 100,000 and -100,000 (without the commas).

Setting the Values
The best manner for setting these is to have your machine move a certain distance (e.g., 1 inch or 10 degrees), and then change this value as necessary to achieve that movement.

Reversing the Direction
If the axis is running in the wrong direction, reverse the polarity of the number (i.e., make a + into a -, or vice versa).</property>
